values: （尤指）鸡蛋；（鸟类的）蛋；（鱼、昆虫等的）卵；卵子；卵细胞；（用作食物的）禽蛋；蛋状物；卵形饰品；（生物学）卵形物

word_group.phrase: put all your eggs in one basket

word_group.brief_definition: 丹配拉画颜料；蛋彩画颜料

bilingual.target: 我每天早上吃一个鸡蛋。

bilingual.source: For breakfast, you can have an egg.
bilingual.target: 早餐你可以吃一个鸡蛋。

bilingual.source: Place the egg in a pan of boiling water.
bilingual.target: 把鸡蛋放在一锅沸水中。

bilingual.source: Quickly put the egg on top of the bottle.
bilingual.target: 快速将鸡蛋放在瓶口上。

bilingual.source: An egg, milk and bread are great for breakfast.
bilingual.target: 鸡蛋、牛奶和面包是很好的早餐。

bilingual.source: For breakfast, I usually have a pie and an egg.
bilingual.target: 早餐我通常吃一个馅饼和一个鸡蛋。

bilingual.source: I usually have an egg and some pancakes or baozi.
bilingual.target: 我通常吃一个鸡蛋和一些煎饼或包子。

bilingual.source: Here are noodles with tomato and egg.

list.abstract: egg，英文单词，做名词时，指鸡蛋、卵细胞；做不及物动词时，指怂恿、煽动、向……掷鸡蛋。其复数形式为eggs，过去式为egged，现在分词为egging。

姓名: Busakon Tantiphana
昵称: egg
职业: 演员/模特/主持人
生日: 7. 12 2531 (1988. 12. 7)
出生地: 曼谷
身高: 160
婚否 : 单身
教育程度 : Chulalongkorn大学 (2011毕业)

yingyinNormal.en: Hello, egg. You gonna introduce us, Riley?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你好，鸡蛋，你要介绍我们认识吗，莱丽？

yingyinNormal.en: Now, I add an egg. Now, the milk. And I give it all a stir.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在，我要加一个鸡蛋。现在，牛奶。我要搅拌一下。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, we're doing the whole "take care of an egg" thing? 'Cause I've seen this.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好了，我现在在做的是照顾鸡蛋这件事，因为我见过。

yingyinNormal.en: Between Mrs. Steuby and Mrs. Helms, my egg overflow problem was solved.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在斯特比和海姆斯太太的帮助下，鸡蛋过多的难题总算得以解决。

yingyinNormal.en: My, my. Something smells good. Alfred's making tarts with an egg and cheese filling.
yingyinNormal.zh: 天啊，什么东西那么香。阿尔弗雷德在做鸡蛋奶酪蛋挞。

yingyinNormal.en: In with a little bit of oil, and there are many different ways of making egg fried rice, OK? I like to cook the egg, almost like scramble it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 倒一点点油，做蛋炒饭有很多种方法。我喜欢先炒鸡蛋，只要搅来搅去就可以了。

yingyinNormal.en: Now you just feel guilty because of the whole egg thing. Yeah, and I insulted her yard.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是因为扔鸡蛋的事有负罪感。嗯，我还侮辱她的院子了。

yingyinNormal.en: This is an egg you knew for a minute. We're giving you responsibility for our child.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是一颗你刚认识一分钟的鸡蛋，我们把照顾孩子的责任交给你。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, with this recipe you can make two omelettes, so I've just put half in, and at this point, when the egg is slightly bubbling to the side of the wok, just tilt the wok and start to distribute, you see, the raw egg that's in the center around the wok, to create your omelette.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这样的用量可以做两个蛋卷，所以我只倒一半，当你看到鸡蛋的边缘起泡泡的时候就可以倾斜锅子，把中心的鸡蛋液向周围摊开，这样才能做成蛋卷。

yingyinNormal.en: See Emily Elephant juggle potatos and an egg. Now last look at Pedro Pony, he is a clown.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看，大象艾米丽用照片和鸡蛋耍把戏。最后，请看小马佩德罗，他是个小丑。

yingyinNormal.en: What, is it secret? No, it's a nitrogen laser. It'll cook your eyeball like a soft-boiled egg.
yingyinNormal.zh: 干嘛，是秘密吗？不，是氮激光器，看一眼，你的眼珠就会变成半熟的鸡蛋。

yingyinNormal.en: Face it Caroline, you came here to humiliate me and you can't even afford that egg. On your face.
yingyinNormal.zh: 承认吧，卡洛琳，你是来羞辱我的，结果丢人到付不起鸡蛋，真是丢死人。

yingyinNormal.en: So, what's next? We'll add egg and cheese to the white sauce, if Mrs Patmore doesn't mind.
yingyinNormal.zh: 下一步怎么做？我们要把鸡蛋和奶酪加到白汁里面，如果帕特莫太太不介意的话。

yingyinNormal.en: We start with butter and sugar and flour, then we add an egg, and most important of all, the chocolate bits.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第一步要放黄油，糖，还有面粉，然后还有鸡蛋。最后最重要的是把巧克力放进去。

yingyinNormal.en: We start with butter and sugar and flour, then we add an egg, and most important of all, the chocolate bits.
yingyinNormal.zh: 第一步要放黄油，糖，还有面粉，然后还有鸡蛋。最后最重要的是把巧克力放进去。

yingyinNormal.en: I'd be trapped inside a huge egg and this monster would open his jaws and start to devour me. I'd wake up just in time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 梦见自己被困在巨型鸡蛋里，怪物张嘴将我吞入囊中，所幸每次都能及时醒来。

yingyinNormal.en: In with some light soy sauce, about two tablespoons. Some toasted sesame oil, and in with a tablespoon of corn flour. And in with a beaten egg.
yingyinNormal.zh: 再加约两汤匙生抽，一点芝麻油，再加约一汤匙玉米淀粉，再加一个打散的鸡蛋。

yingyinNormal.en: Once scrambled, set the cooked egg to one side. Then put the grated ginger into the smoking wok. Vegetables follow. The chopped ham. Spring onions and bean sprouts. Pretty much that's ready.
yingyinNormal.zh: 鸡蛋炒好后，放在一边，然后把生姜末放进热锅中。接着放蔬菜，接着是切好的火腿，葱和豆芽，这差不多就好了。

yingyinNormal.en: I need the kettle cos I need to cook my noodles. In with my egg noodles, great. Just drain. Look, lovely and bouncy and fresh.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要用开水，因为要做我的面。加入鸡蛋面，很好。沥干。色香俱全，弹性十足，非常新鲜。

yingyinNormal.en: These are what I call noodles, the real authentic noodles, mung bean noodles, rice noodles, egg noodles and my favorite, we've got the yellow shi noodle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这些才是面条，真正的面条：绿豆粉丝、米线、鸡蛋面和我最爱的细面。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: It can be learned from the last paragraph that young people are likely to buy climate-friendly <highlight>eggs</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 从上一段可以了解到，年轻人很可能会购买气候友好型鸡蛋。

examination_example.sentence: Such <highlight>eggs</highlight> could be marketed as helping to fight climate change.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这种鸡蛋可以作为帮助对抗气候变化的商品进行销售。

examination_example.sentence: Such farming also brings minimal, if any, improvement to the food products (though some producers say their <highlight>eggs</highlight> have more protein).
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这种养殖方式给食品带来的改善极小，即使有也是微乎其微(尽管一些生产商说他们的鸡蛋含有更多的蛋白质)。
